                     <interp inst="t18431127-159-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 8 printed books, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18431127-name-885" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-885" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
